      "rationale": "The constitutive model (isotropic elastic with neo-Hookean contact) is appropriate for UHMWPE under quasi-static loading at the strain rates present in ISO 14243-1 gait cycles. Viscoelastic effects are negligible at 1 Hz loading frequency per published UHMWPE rheology data. Model form uncertainty was assessed by comparing elastic vs. elastic-plastic formulations; difference in peak contact stress < 3% under COU loading magnitudes, confirming elastic model adequacy.",
